3:["$","p","1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base","children":"We combine passive range-of-motion stretching with Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation (NMES) to keep muscles active. Proprioceptive Neuromuscular Facilitation (PNF) patterns stimulate nerve pathways, encouraging movement."}]
